dct_title_s: The Former Yugoslav Republic of Macedonia 1:20,000. Skopje. Series M903
dct_description_sm: Alternate title: Skopje. Transverse Mercator projection. Relief shown by 20 meter contour intervals and spot elevation. "This sheet falls within NK 34-5 and NK 34-8, 1501A, 1:250,000 and 3278 I, 3279 II, 3378 IV, 3379 III, M709, 1:50,000." "Map information as of 1984. Embassy and Consulate information as of 1996" Coordinate conversion WGS 84 to ED 50. Reprinted by NIMA 5-99. With a glossary.
